  <brief_title>EURopean Trial In Atrial Fibrillation(AF) or Flutter (AFL) Patients Receiving Dronedarone for the maIntenance of Sinus Rhythm (EURIDIS)</brief_title>
  <acronym>EURIDIS</acronym>
  <official_title>EURopean Trial In Atrial Fibrillation or Flutter Patients Receiving Dronedarone for the maIntenance of Sinus Rhythm (EURIDIS)</official_title>
